trans-unit.source: Lets users select a printer and choose which sections of the document to print from a Windows Forms application.
trans-unit.target: 允许用户选择打印机，然后选择要从 Windows 窗体应用程序打印的文档的哪些部分。

trans-unit.source: When you create an instance of PrintDialog, the read/write properties are set to initial values.
trans-unit.target: 当你创建的 PrintDialog 实例时，读/写属性设置为初始值。

trans-unit.source: For a list of these values, see the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: 有关这些值的列表，请参阅<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.%23ctor%2A>构造函数。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: To get printer settings that are modified by the user with the PrintDialog, use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrinterSettings%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 若要获取由具有 PrintDialog 用户修改的打印机设置，请使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrinterSettings%2A>属性。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrinterSettings%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about printing with Windows Forms, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: 有关打印功能与 Windows 窗体的详细信息，请参阅<xref:System.Drawing.Printing>命名空间概述。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Presentation Foundation application, see the <xref:System.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: 如果你想要从 Windows Presentation Foundation 应用程序打印，请参阅<xref:System.Printing>命名空间。</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog"></xref>类。

trans-unit.source: When you create an instance of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>, the following read/write properties are set to initial values.

trans-unit.source: |Property|Initial Value| |--------------|-------------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSomePages%2A>|`false`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowPrintToFile%2A>|`true`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSelection%2A>|`false`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.Document%2A>|`null`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrinterSettings%2A>|`null`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrintToFile%2A>|`false`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.ShowHelp%2A>|`false`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.ShowNetwork%2A>|`true`| You can change the value for any one of these properties through a separate call to the property.
trans-unit.target: |属性 |初始值 | |--------------|-------------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSomePages%2A>|`false`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowPrintToFile%2A>|`true`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSelection%2A>|`false`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.Document%2A>|`null`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrinterSettings%2A>|`null`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrintToFile%2A>|`false`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.ShowHelp%2A>|`false`| |<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.ShowNetwork%2A>|`true`| 你可以更改的任一通过单独属性调用这些属性的值。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.ShowNetwork%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.ShowHelp%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrintToFile%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrinterSettings%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.Document%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSelection%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowPrintToFile%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSomePages%2A>
